name: Delight in Difference
description: Two worlds are brought together in the hopes that they might help each other, as the Kwejian are brought in to help Capellans, who may be able to repay the favor in the distant future. But could a sinister plot derail this new friendship?
rules:
-- Unique Supply Missions are available during the event. Open the Event to access them.
-- Using Fascination Lwaxana Troi, any version of Maab, Mr. Homn, Kyheem, or Betazoids will provide a bonus to Supply Missions.
-- Every Supply Mission you complete earns you Event Victory Points. Collect Event Victory Points to unlock Threshold Rewards!
-- Community Rewards are only available during Phase 1. Collect Event Victory Points to unlock these rewards before the phase change!
-- In this event, Squadrons may also compete to advance up the Squadron leaderboards. Join a Squadron to get more rewards!
bonus_text: Crew Bonus: Fascination Lwaxana Troi, Maab, Mr. Homn, Kyheem, or Betazoids
rewards_teaser: Reach Rank 1 by gaining Victory Points from Event Supply Missions!

featured_crew.name: Tendi
featured_crew.flavor: An enraged Tendi picks up a strange pink cube that turns her into a huge scorpion.

featured_crew.name: Homn
featured_crew.flavor: Ambassador Troi’s valet. A man of few - or rather no - words. Very attentive, though sometimes it became irritating.

featured_crew.name: Kyheem
featured_crew.flavor: Kyheem serves as Steward of the Sanctuary in order to protect the Kwejian harvests from sea locusts.
